      "updated": 1381768982213,
      "title": "Loyal A4 driver disappointed",
      "text": "This will be my 5th A4 in either a sedan or wagon version.\nWhile the car looks great inside and out and the improved HP over the years has added to the thrill of driving the new electronic steering has certainly been a negative.\nIf you are looking for a soft feel to lumber off to the grocery store the steering is fine but push it a bit or take a long highway trek and you will notice the floaty feel.\nOverall the car is fine but if your a searching for a tight steering / handling feel you may want to give the car a good test drive before you purchase.\nAfter this lease is up I will definetly look at a tighter car like the BMW.",
      "favoriteFeatures": "Interior and exterior design, AWD system",
      "suggestedImprovements": "Offer an option to the electronic steering that was introduced in 2013.\nOffer Blind Spot on the Premium as an option.",
