      "created": 1354163622006,
      "updated": 0,
      "title": "Best bang for your buck for an AWD luxury sedan",
      "text": "This is my second Audi. I upgraded from a 2012 Audi A4 2.0T FWD with CVT. It was a great car. Great performance and gas mileage.\nHowever, I had an opportunity to upgrade to a quattro with the light package and 2013 upgrades. So far, the car is awesome. Drives even better with the Quattro and suspension and steering upgrades. And those lights, beautiful. The car is even more stricking then my 2012. I also like the 8 speed auto better then the CVT.",
      "favoriteFeatures": "Love the Quattro. It feels so planted. I also love the LED light package. And it's a great design for a\nsedan;better then both the BMW and Mercedes. Neither can beat the interior design and it's fit and finish. Great gas mileage too. Oh, and that turbo, so much fun to drive.\nGreat all around car.",
      "suggestedImprovements": "I wish it had BT audio and USB port. ",
